Everyday we have register then go to phonics into 10:45 then we come back to litercyfr half a nhour then its break time Mr.Stirling is my teacher i think he is a great teacher he is funny. the after break we go to maths, maths is fun i am in year five it is fun (TRUST ME IT IS FUN) we go gardening after lunch with Mr.Naylor he is a great gardenor . Danique louise Renshaw
